Woody Medlock, Sr., 70, and his wife, Kathy Medlock, 58, of Murfreesboro, Tennessee, former owners of Murfreesboro Ambulance Service, were sentenced yesterday to federal prison for Medicare fraud and aggravated identity theft, announced David Rivera, U.S. Attorney for the Middle District of Tennessee. </dd>

