<dd><a class="exit" href="http://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/2014/January/14-civ-037.html">Government Intervenes In Lawsuits against Health Management Associates Inc. Hospital Chain Alleging Unnecessary Inpatient Admissions and Payment of Kickbacks</a><br />
